Ngentwasahlobo ka - 33 C.E . , uJesu waseNarazetha wabulawa .
Wayebekwe icala lokukhuthaza abantu ukuba bavukele umbuso , washaywa ngesihluku futhi wabethelwa esigxotsheni .
Kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa futhi ngemva kwezinsuku ezingu - 40 uJesu wanyukela ezulwini .
Lokhu kulandisa okungavamile kutholakala emaVangelini amane emiBhalo yamaKristu yesiGreki , ngokuvamile abizwa ngokuthi iTestamente Elisha .
Ngakolunye uhlangothi , uma lezo zenzakalo zenzeka ngempela , lokho kusho ukuthi abantu banekusasa eliqhakazile , nawe ongahlanganyela kulo .
Pho , ingabe ukulandisa kwamaVangeli kuyiqiniso noma kuyinganekwane ?
Ngokungafani nezinganekwane ezithandwayo , amaVangeli alotshwa ngokunembile futhi kwanakisiswa ngisho nemininingwane emincane .
Ngokwesibonelo , amaVangeli aqukethe amagama ezindawo zangempela , eziningi zazo ongazivakashela nanamuhla .
Akhuluma ngabantu abangokoqobo , izazi zomlando eziye zalandisa ngabo . — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Ababhali abaziwayo bangekhulu lokuqala nelesibili leminyaka bakhuluma ngoJesu .
* Indlela afa ngayo echazwe emaVangelini , ivumelana nendlela amaRoma ayebulala ngayo izelelesi ngaleso sikhathi .
Ngaphezu kwalokho , izenzakalo zilandiswe njengoba zinjalo , kwangasala lutho — kuze kulandiswe nangezinto ezimbi ezazenziwa abalandeli bakaJesu .
Konke lokhu kukufakazela ngokuqinile ukuthi abalobi bamaVangeli babethembekile futhi benembile kulokho ababekuloba ngoJesu .
Nakuba abaningi bevuma ukuthi uJesu waphila futhi wafa , abanye bayakungabaza ukuvuswa kwakhe .
Ngisho nabaphostoli bakhe abazange bayikholelwe imibiko yokuqala yokuthi uvusiwe .
Nokho , lokho kungabaza kwaphela lapho bona nabanye abaphostoli bebona uJesu ovusiwe ngezikhathi ezahlukahlukene .
Empeleni , ngesinye isikhathi , wabonakala kubantu abangaphezu kuka - 500 ngesikhathi esisodwa . — 1 Korinte 15 : 6 .
Bezibeka engozini yokuboshwa noma yokubulawa , ngesibindi abafundi bamemezela ngokuvuswa kukaJesu kubo bonke — ngisho nakulabo abambulala .
Ingabe abafundi abaningi kangaka babengaba nesibindi esikhulu kangaka ukube babengaqiniseki ukuthi uJesu uvusiwe ngempela ?
Empeleni ukwazi ukuthi uJesu wavuswa , yikona ngokuyinhloko okuye kwabangela ukuba ubuKristu bube nethonya emhlabeni kusukela ngaleso sikhathi kuze kube namuhla .
Ukulandisa kwamaVangeli ngokufa nokuvuswa kukaJesu kusinikeza ubufakazi obuqand ’ ikhanda bokuthi kunembile ngokomlando .
Ukukufunda ngokucophelela kuzokuqinisekisa ngokuthi lezi zenzakalo zenzeka ngempela .
Ukuqonda ukuthi kungani lezi zenzakalo zenzeka kungakwenza uqiniseke ngisho nakakhulu .
UTacitus owazalwa cishe ngo - 55 C.E . , waloba ukuthi “ uKristu , ” okususelwa kuye igama elithi amaKristu , wakhuthazelela isigwebo esibuhlungu phakathi nokubusa kukaTiberiyu eshushiswa omunye wezikhulu zethu uPontiyu Pilatu . ”
Abanye abantu abakhuluma ngoJesu , uSuetonius ( ngekhulu lokuqala ) ; isazi - mlando esingumJuda uJosephus ( ngekhulu lokuqala ) noPliny the Younger umbusi waseBhithiniya ( ekuqaleni kwekhulu lesibili ) .
Kubonakala sengathi mancane amathuba okuthi abaphikisi bakaJesu abaningi babengabhala izinto ezinhle ngaye .
Ngokuphathelene nokuvuswa kukaJesu , omunye wabaphostoli bakhe uPetru wachaza : “ UNkulunkulu wamvusa lo ngosuku lwesithathu futhi wamvumela ukuba abonakale , hhayi kubo bonke abantu , kodwa kofakazi abamiswa uNkulunkulu kusengaphambili , kithi , esadla futhi saphuza naye ngemva kokuvuka kwakhe kwabafileyo . ”
IVangeli likaMathewu lisitshela ukuthi lapho izitha zenkolo zizwa imibiko yokuvuswa kukaJesu , zazama ukuthulisa ababesakaza leyo mibiko . — Mathewu 28 : 11 - 15 .
Ingabe lokho kusho ukuthi uJesu wayefuna ukuvuswa kwakhe kube yimfihlo ?
Cha , ngoba uPetru waqhubeka wathi : “ Wasiyala ukuba sishumayele kubantu , sinikeze ubufakazi obuphelele bokuthi lo nguYe uNkulunkulu anquma ukuba abe umahluleli wabaphilayo nabafileyo . ”
AmaKristu eqiniso aye akwenza lokho futhi ayaqhubeka ekwenza . — IzEnzo 10 : 42 .
“ Ngomuntu oyedwa [ u - Adamu ] isono sangena ezweni nokufa kwangena ngesono . ” — Roma 5 : 12 .
Ubungathini uma ungabuzwa ukuthi , “ Uyafuna yini ukuphila phakade ? ”
Cishe abantu abaningi bebengathi bayafuna kodwa banomuzwa wokuthi into enjalo ayinakwenzeka .
Bathi ukufa kuyingxenye yokuphila , isiphetho sokuphila kwethu .
Nokho , ake sithi manje ubuzwa ukuthi , “ Ukulungele yini ukufa ? ”
Ezimweni ezivamile , abantu abaningi bangathi cha .
IBhayibheli libonisa ukuthi uNkulunkulu wadala abantu benesifiso sokuphila .
Empeleni , lithi ‘ ufake ngisho nobuphakade ezinhliziyweni zabo . ’ — UmShumayeli 3 : 11 .
Nokho , iqiniso liwukuthi abantu abaphili phakade .
Ngaphezu kwalokho , ingabe kukhona uNkulunkulu akwenzile ukuze alungise lesi simo ?
Izimpendulo zeBhayibheli zithinta inhliziyo futhi zikuveza ngokucacile ukuthi kungani uJesu ahlupheka futhi wafa .
Izahluko ezintathu zokuqala zencwadi kaGenesise zisitshela ukuthi uNkulunkulu wanikeza umbhangqwana wokuqala ithemba lokuphila phakade futhi wawuchazela lokho okufanele ukwenze ukuze uthole lokho kuphila .
Ukulandisa kube sekuchaza indlela lo mbhangqwana owahluleka ngayo ukulalela uNkulunkulu futhi walahlekelwa yilelo themba .
Le ndaba ilandiswa ngendlela elula , kangangokuba abanye bavele bathi iyinganekwane .
NjengamaVangeli , incwadi kaGenesise inikeza ubufakazi obuqand ’ ikhanda bokuthi lokhu kulandisa kwenzeka ngempela .
Uye waba yini umphumela wokungalaleli kuka - Adamu ?
IBhayibheli liphendula ngale ndlela : “ Ngomuntu oyedwa [ u - Adamu ] isono sangena ezweni nokufa kwangena ngesono , futhi kanjalo ukufa kwasakazekela kubantu bonke ngenxa yokuthi bonke bonile . ”
Ngaleyo ndlela walahlekelwa ithuba lokuphila phakade futhi ekugcineni wafa .
Njengenzalo yakhe , siye sazuza isono njengefa .
Kodwa - ke , ingabe kukhona uNkulunkulu akwenzile ukuze alungise lesi simo ?
Yebo , uNkulunkulu wenze amalungiselelo okubuyisa lokho okuye kwalahlekela inzalo ka - Adamu , okungukuthi ithemba lokuphila phakade .
KweyabaseRoma 6 : 23 , iBhayibheli lithi : “ Inkokhelo yesono ngukufa . ”
Lokhu kusho ukuthi ukufa kubangelwa isono .
Ngokufanayo , siyona futhi ngenxa yalokho sithola inkokhelo yesono , ewukufa .
Nakuba singonanga , sazalwa sinesono .
Ngakho , ngothando uNkulunkulu wathumela iNdodana yakhe , uJesu , ukuze isikhulule esonweni .
Ukufa kukaJesu kuvula indlela eholela ekuphileni okuphakade okujabulisayo
Njengoba u - Adamu , indoda ephelele eyodwa , aletha isono nokufa ngokungalaleli , kwakudingeka indoda eyodwa ephelele ezolalela kuze kube sekugcineni ukuze isikhulule .
IBhayibheli likuchaza ngale ndlela : “ Njengoba nje ngokungalaleli komuntu oyedwa abaningi baba yizoni , ngokufanayo futhi ngokulalela komuntu oyedwa abaningi bayoba ngabalungileyo . ”
Washiya izulu , waba indoda ephelele * futhi wafa ngenxa yethu .
Ngenxa yalokho , singakwazi ukuthandeka emehlweni kaNkulunkulu futhi sithole ithuba lokuphila phakade .
Kungani kwakudingeka uJesu afe ukuze afeze lokho ?
UNkulunkulu uMninimandla onke wayengeke yini akwazi ukumane akhiphe umyalo wokuba inzalo ka - Adamu ivunyelwe ukuba iphile phakade ?
Ukube uNkulunkulu ubenze ngendlela engenabulungisa kule ndaba , abantu bebeyolindela ukuba enze okufanayo nakwezinye izinto .
Ngokwesibonelo , bekungaba ubulungisa yini ukuba anqume ukuthi obani enzalweni ka - Adamu abafanelekela ukuthola ukuphila okuphakade ?
Besingamethemba yini ukuba agcwalise izithembiso zakhe ?
Ukwenza ngobulungisa ekunqumeni ukuthi obani abayosinda kusiqinisekisa ngokuthi uNkulunkulu uyohlale enza okulungile .
Ngokufa kukaJesu okuwumhlatshelo , uNkulunkulu wavula indlela yokuthola ukuphila phakade emhlabeni oyiPharadesi .
Phawula amazwi kaJesu alotshwe kuJohane 3 : 16 : “ UNkulunkulu walithanda izwe kangangokuba waze wanikela ngeNdodana yakhe ezelwe yodwa , ukuze wonke umuntu obonisa ukholo kuyo angabhubhi kodwa abe nokuphila okuphakade . ”
Ngakho , ukufa kukaJesu akugcini nje ngokusibonisa ubulungisa bukaNkulunkulu obuphelele , kodwa ngokukhethekile kusibonisa uthando olukhulu analo ngabantu .
Nokho , kungani kwadingeka ukuba uJesu ahlupheke futhi afe kabuhlungu njengoba kuchazwe emaVangelini ?
Ngokubekezelela uvivinyo olunzima nangokuzigcina ethembekile , uJesu wafakazela ukuthi uSathane unamanga uma ethi abantu ngeke bakwazi ukuhlale beqotho kuNkulunkulu lapho bebhekene novivinyo .
Amazwi kaSathane ayengase abonakale eyiqiniso ngemva kokuba elinge u - Adamu ophelele ukuba one .
Kodwa uJesu — owayephelele njengo - Adamu — waqhubeka ethembekile naphezu kobunzima obukhulu ayebhekene nabo .
Ngaleyo ndlela wabonisa ukuthi no - Adamu wayengamlalela uNkulunkulu uma ayekhetha ukwenza kanjalo .
Ngokukhuthazelela uvivinyo , uJesu wasishiyela isibonelo sokulingiswa .
UNkulunkulu wayivuza iNdodana yakhe ephelele , uJesu , ngokulalela kwayo , wayinika ukuphila okungenakufa ezulwini .
UJesu wabonisa lokho okudingeka sikwenze lapho ethi : “ Lokhu kusho ukuphila okuphakade , ukungenisa kwabo ulwazi ngawe , owukuphela kukaNkulunkulu weqiniso , nangalowo omthumileyo , uJesu Kristu . ” — Johane 17 : 3 .
Abanyathelisi balo magazini bakumema ukuba ufunde okwengeziwe ngoJehova , uNkulunkulu weqiniso , nangeNdodana yakhe , uJesu Kristu .
